      <title>南非财政部长表示新规则是改善财务状况的关键</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/south-african-finance-chief-says-new-rules-key-to-mend-finances</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非财政部长表示，引入财政规则是有意义的，因为持续断电和后勤限制导致的经济增长停滞阻碍了控制不断膨胀的债务的努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/south-african-finance-chief-says-new-rules-key-to-mend-finances</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 17:21:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
