      <title>美国因人权问题制裁津巴布韦总统姆南加古瓦</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/us-sanctions-zimbabwe-president-mnangagwa-over-human-rights-ltd5sfv4</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国正在对津巴布韦总统埃默森·姆南加古瓦和其他高级官员实施制裁，称其在有争议的选举后存在“严重滥用职权”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/us-sanctions-zimbabwe-president-mnangagwa-over-human-rights-ltd5sfv4</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 16:31:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国谴责美国在电动汽车紧张局势中采取“经典保护主义”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/china-blasts-us-for-classic-protectionism-in-tension-over-evs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国指责美国采取保护主义贸易措施，有迹象表明华盛顿准备加大力度阻止中国电动汽车进入美国市场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-04/china-blasts-us-for-classic-protectionism-in-tension-over-evs</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 16:24:11 GMT</pubDate>
